{"tid":2514436,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁國雄被押解到明愛醫院 獲支持巿民點頭問好","createTime":"2021-05-03T09:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T09:14:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8678a08a9273f292bbf53511b3e1c67187687e","tid":2514436,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iJTEyGmFlcfNoTsa0vdXU255o7Q=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LHMHMSBBG5DO5IMQ67V6EF5TBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiJTEyGmFlcfNoTsa0vdXU255o7Q%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLHMHMSBBG5DO5IMQ67V6EF5TBA.jpg&h=9c4b65e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n65歲「長毛」梁國雄，因8.18和平遊行被控組織及參與未經批准集結，上月中被判罪成重囚18個月，今日下午約3時半，讀者江小姐在明愛醫院懷明樓3樓內科門診赫見長毛在場候診，他由懲教署人員押解、腰纏鎖鏈及鎖上手銬，進入其中一個診症室。<br />\n<br />\n江小姐眼見長毛體形消瘦，在診症室內逗留10至15分鐘後由懲教人員押走，但未幾醫生走出來找其蹤影，長毛再次被帶入診症室，數分鐘後離開，前往藥房取藥。在場候診人士，有支持者向長毛點頭問好，長毛亦點頭微笑示意。江小姐直言，覺得長毛「瘦咗好多」，希望他在獄中撐住。<br />\n<br />\n社民連主席黃浩銘表示，以他所知，長毛於3月初47子參與民主派初選案因馬拉松聆訊，曾不支暈倒送院，因此今日需前往明愛醫院覆診。3月1日，47名因參與民主派初選而被控「串謀顛覆國家政權」的民主派人士，面對14小時馬拉松式聆訊，並無進食下，一眾被告疲憊不堪，終捱至翌日凌晨2時許，首先女被告楊雪盈不適暈倒，其後譚凱邦及梁國雄等陸續不支送院。<br />\n<br />\n此外，前年8月18日大量市民參加民陣在維園的流水式集會，大雨中和平爭取五大訴求。黎智英、李卓人等9名泛民人士被控當天組織及參與未經批准遊行，梁國雄被判罪成，刑期最長重囚18個月。據知，長毛患有冠心病，三條血管中兩條栓塞逾5成，需每日接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210503/ZCDUXMLK7JGFRCX4QB6DH2AH5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210503%2FZCDUXMLK7JGFRCX4QB6DH2AH5A%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOM04bh6pArHnk2fwDmvpgUU%3D&h=3d0838ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210503%2FZCDUXMLK7JGFRCX4QB6DH2AH5A%2F&h=a19ea27d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210503/ZCDUXMLK7JGFRCX4QB6DH2AH5A/</a>"},{"pid":"71f30d9a520f2f1239ff6ab0523b1418a50fe2e8","tid":2514436,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4414ae04940e04b3c0c6a8095351ba879a97f309","tid":2514436,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母班柳記折磨到佢得返皮包骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354bcf6b0dfb3cd2f2b62e5ea729b2e003099eab","tid":2514436,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6cb94c7f6e3e7ca0c58847c01d667bbe0d24122","tid":2514436,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}